description:
Urinosuke is a creature that looks like wild boar piglet, that hatched from an egg which got attached to http://anidb.net/ch90644 [Ren] and http://anidb.net/ch90643 [Satsuki]. It occasionally feeds on nightmares of the residents of Konohanatai.
According to http://anidb.net/ch90639 [Yuzu], Urinosuke could be baku - supernatural being that devours dreams and nightmares in Japanese folklore.
name: Urinosuke
